            <div class="article-contributor__meta-container">
              <h1 class="article-contributor-section_title">Denise Rose Hansen</h1>
              <p class="article-contributor-section_content">Denise Rose Hansen is a Danish writer and editor who lives in London. The founder of Lolli Editions, she is now an editor at Penguin where she publishes the likes of Shahrnush Parsipur, Ágota Kristóf, and Anne Serre.</p>
